<div class="com-share" data-id="1480" data-title="《「这世界」美国人居然开始嘲笑英国人无知了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1480/medium/1480.jpg?1436641660" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1480" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
